

<div class="container my-5">
  <div class="row p-4 pb-0 pe-lg-0 pt-lg-5 align-items-center rounded-3 border shadow-lg">
    <div class="col-lg-7 p-3 p-lg-5 pt-lg-3">
      <h1 id="changeColor" class="display-4 fw-bold lh-1"><i>Stay on Track:</i>
        <br>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-list-ul"></i>
         ToDoList it!
      </h1>

      <p class="lead">Never miss a deadline!  Break projects into manageable pieces. Tackle important tasks first. Celebrate the small wins. ToDoList it!</p>
      <div class="row mb-5">
        <span class="lead">View tasks  <i class="fa-regular fa-folder-open" style="color:#26D95D; font-size: 150%" ></i></span>
